race.comment: MR ASSERTIVE (7) has ability but facing a long drought. Has worked back into fitness and been runner-up last two. Rawiller back aboard and will take catching. GUNDAROO (3) has been safely held last couple but in much tougher grade. Is well placed here and gets chance to find some form. TAPO (4) raced on pace and fought on well last time to finish runner-up. Aided by the claim and will give a sight again. SUB GAUGE (6) is another fitter for two runs back and has won third run back. Heavy track winner last time and all best form has been in rain-affected going. Tricky gate but expected to run well.
race.rail_position: +4m from the 400m to the winning post, True Remainder. (Pent: 5.60)
